General.Name: Scorpio Tankers Inc
General.Description: Scorpio Tankers Inc., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the seaborne transportation of crude oil and refined petroleum products worldwide. As of March 20, 2025, its fleet consisted of 99 owned and leased financed tankers, including 38 LR2, 47 MR, and 14 Handymax. Scorpio Tankers Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Monaco.
